*Trebamo* da se sastanemo zajedno (We need to meet together).
*Oni *trebaju* da se pridržavaju propisa (They need to adhere to the regulations).
*Mi *trebamo* da radimo naš posao (We need to do our job).
*Njemu *treba* pomoć (He needs help).
*Moramo *trebati* jedni drugima (We need to need each other).